original_title: Bob the Builder: Dig! Lift! Haul!
overview: While carrying cement to Farmer Pickles, Muck passes through a field and hears a howling noise coming from a hole in the ground. When Bob and Lofty go digging for the answer, what will they find is making the strange noise?
tagline: Haul In The Fun With 5 Exciting Adventures!
title: Bob the Builder: Dig! Lift! Haul!
